**ResearchHub Endowments**  
Turn the $RSC in your ResearchHub account into a perpetual science funding machine

| Tl;Dr \- Hold ResearchCoin ($RSC) in your ResearchHub account and automatically earn \~5-25% yearly returns in funding credits. Use these credits to fund preregistered research proposals.  |
| :---- |

**How It Works**

| 01 Hold ResearchCoin Deposit newly purchased $RSC into your ResearchHub account.  | 02 Earn Credits Automatically The $RSC you hold earns yield funded via protocol inflation.  | 03 Fund Science Donate the funding credits you earned & earn a tax break. |
| :---- | :---- | :---- |

| Self-Balancing Yield Funding credit yield is dynamic over time. Initially less RSC will be staked, so the yield will be higher. As more RSC is deposited into ResearchHub the yield decreases, until it stabilizes at a rate the market considers fair.
